---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import SectionTitle from "../components/SectionTitle.astro";
---
<Base title="Method — Historical Translation Project™">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 py-14 sm:py-20">
    <SectionTitle
      eyebrow="Method"
      title="A repeatable translation pipeline"
      subtitle="We build an expandable architecture so new traditions, new books, and new formulations slot in cleanly—without rewriting the site every time."
    />
    <div class="mt-12 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/70 ring-1 ring-black/5 shadow-card p-8">
        <div class="font-display text-2xl">1) Historical foundations</div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-lg text-ink/75 leading-relaxed">
          Primary texts → annotated excerpts → practical principles. We preserve the historical voice, but we do not treat it as medical advice.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/70 ring-1 ring-black/5 shadow-card p-8">
        <div class="font-display text-2xl">2) Modern evidence overview</div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-lg text-ink/75 leading-relaxed">
          Safety signals, plausibility, and conservative summaries of modern research—presented in structure/function language.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/70 ring-1 ring-black/5 shadow-card p-8">
        <div class="font-display text-2xl">3) Formula logic</div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-lg text-ink/75 leading-relaxed">
          We design daily foundations, then reserve add‑ons for targeted needs not already addressed by a program—minimizing redundancy and SKUs.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/70 ring-1 ring-black/5 shadow-card p-8">
        <div class="font-display text-2xl">4) Transparent pages & dossiers</div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-lg text-ink/75 leading-relaxed">
          Every program page follows the same structure: overview → foundations → modern overview → ingredient story → add‑ons → cautions.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
